DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
     _G_e_t_l_o_g_i_n returns a pointer to the login name as found in
     /_e_t_c/_u_t_m_p.  It may be used in conjunction with _g_e_t_p_w_n_a_m to
     locate the correct password file entry when the same userid
