     If _g_e_t_l_o_g_i_n is called within a process that is not attached
     to a terminal, or if there is no entry in /_e_t_c/_u_t_m_p for the
     process's terminal, _g_e_t_l_o_g_i_n returns a NULL pointer (0).  A
